events.name: Repair Kopitiam - 22nd January 2017
events.description:
Chinese New Year is coming! Let's not throw away those spoilt electrical appliances, instead, try fixing it WITH US!
Our Repair Coaches will be there to TEACH you how to repair them!
Bring your family and learn how to repair together in this free event!
